    dc:title "A new schistosome (Digenea: Schistosomatidae) from the nasal tissue of South America black-necked swans, Cygnus melancoryphus (Anatidae) and the endemic pulmonate snail Chilina gibbosa" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629164>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629166>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629168>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629160> ;
